data.description: Looking for a stunning home in El Lago, TX? Look no further than 403 Pebblebrook Drive! This elegant and spacious property boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, making it the perfect fit for you.  Inside, you'll find a beautifully appointed interior with a formal living room and dining room, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying dinner. The chefs kitchen is a dream come true for any home cook, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, plenty of storage, and a cozy breakfast area where you can enjoy your morning coffee. But that's not all – step outside and you'll find a large back yard, just waiting to be transformed into your own personal oasis. With room for a pool, you can enjoy endless summer days soaking up the sun, or host a fun-filled pool party with family and friends.  403 Pebblebrook Drive is truly a one-of-a-kind property that you don't want to miss. So why wait? Schedule a showing today and start living the life you've always dreamed of!
